Description: Using this ticket to track engineering progress on finding from customer where after exporting the DB from their on-prem server and importing into the new SaaS environment, it was found that the Endpoint Protector Rights Functionality Priority setting was not overwritten by the DB import. Solution_Comment__c: Closing ticket as questions were answered.
